<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Listing Submitted — AddressGuru</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f6f7fb;
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
      color: #333333;
    }
    .wrapper {
      width: 100%;
      background-color: #f6f7fb;
      padding: 40px 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      background: #ffffff;
      margin: auto;
      border-radius: 14px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f7941d, #ffb347);
      text-align: center;
      padding: 30px 20px;
      color: #ffffff;
    }
    .header img {
      width: 150px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .header h1 {
      font-size: 22px;
      margin: 0;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.4px;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 30px 25px;
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333333;
    }
    .content p {
      margin: 15px 0;
    }
    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f7941d, #ffb347);
      color: #ffffff !important;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 14px 28px;
      border-radius: 50px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-top: 25px;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
    .btn:hover {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff9e35, #ffb347);
      box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(247,148,29,0.3);
    }
    .footer {
      background-color: #fafafa;
      padding: 25px 20px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #777777;
      border-top: 1px solid #eee;
    }
    .footer a {
      color: #f7941d;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 500;
    }
    .footer a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
    @media (max-width: 480px) {
      .content {
        padding: 20px 15px;
      }
      .btn {
        width: 100%;
        text-align: center;
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <a href="https://addressguru.ae" target="_blank">
          <img src="https://www.addressguru.in/images/logopng.png" alt="AddressGuru Logo">
        </a>
        <h1>Listing Submitted Successfully</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <p>Hi <strong>{{userName}}</strong>,</p>
        <p>
          Your listing <strong>“{{listingTitle}}”</strong> has been submitted successfully. Our team will review it shortly.
        </p>
        <p>
          You will receive another email once it’s approved and published.
        </p>
        <p style="text-align:center;">
          <a href="{{listingUrl}}" class="btn" target="_blank">View Listing</a>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        &copy; {{year}} AddressGuru. All rights reserved. <br>
        <a href="https://addressguru.ae" target="_blank">addressguru.ae</a> | <a href="mailto:support@addressguru.ae">support@addressguru.ae</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
